author: Source: The Chronicle Herald
title: Jose Bautista's blast sends Blue Jays to Game 5 victory - The Chronicle Herald
text:
Capping a deciding game filled with controversy, bad blood and just plain craziness, Jose Bautista's three-run homer propelled the Blue Jays into the American League Championship Series as baseball karma delivered Toronto a wild 6-3 win over the Texas Rangers on Wednesday. Game 5 of the AL Division Series was filled with drama - and almost as much talk as play on the field before a riled-up sellout crowd of 49,742 under the Rogers Centre roof.
 The Chronicle Herald.
